<div class="top-element about-top">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="column sm-12">
            <h1 class="about-top__title h1-font">About <br /> Dr. Amer Al Rawas</h1>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="about-block">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="column sm-12 md-7 lg-5">
            <div class="about-block__text">
                <div class="text">
                    Dr. Amer Al Rawas is an award-winning Omani leader, business consultant, executive coach,
                    and public speaker who thrives on helping others to reach their goals while leading fuller, richer, more fulfilling lives.
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    Born and raised in Salalah, Oman’s third largest city, he has traveled extensively in pursuing his own work,
                    study, and personal objectives. He sees each new experience as an opportunity to learn and teach, develop his
                    emotional intelligence, gain new perspectives, and build mutual understanding by appreciating the particulars
                    of different sectors, subjects, and cultures.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="about-block__bottom">
                <div class="highlight_md bordered-text bordered-text_outside">
                    Dr. Rawas began his overseas education by earning a Higher National Diploma
                    in Software Engineering from the University of Brighton in the United Kingdom.
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    He also obtained a BS in Computer Science and a PhD in Computer Science and Artificial
                    Intelligence (AI), both from the UK’s University of Sussex, and was a Visiting Scholar
                    and Researcher at the NASA-West Virginia University Software Research Laboratory in the United States.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column sm-12 md-5 lg-7">
            <div class="about-block__preview">
                <div class="about-block__img">
                    <img src="assets/img/test/dr-amer.jpg" alt="Dr. Amer">
                </div>
                <div class="about-block__decor">
                    <div class="decor-text decor-font color-main after-element">
                        <div class="decor-text__content">Working to live is normal and healthy; living to work is neither.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="about-section">
    <div class="row align-between">
        <div class="column sm-12 lg-6">
            <div class="about-section__main">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="column sm-12 md-6 lg-12">
                        <div class="about-section__heading">
                            <h2 class="about-section__title h2-font">Evolution of a Transformational Leader</h2>
                            <div class="text">
                                Even before completing his PhD, Dr. Rawas had worked for several years at the Omani
                                Ministry of Petroleum and Minerals, serving as Personal Assistant to the Minister.
                                As his formal studies came to a close, he returned to his homeland determined to help
                                it navigate the challenges of comprehensive modernization.
                            </div>
                            <div class="text">
                                He returned to the ministry as Planning Advisor and helped reorganize it under an
                                Oil & Gas mandate, but his early grasp of technologies – especially artificial intelligence –
                                and their implications soon attracted him to new opportunities in sectors across the economy.
                                Thus began a remarkable journey that has made Dr. Rawas one of Oman’s most respected business
                                figures, a can-do leader, speaker, coach, and consultant who gets transformational things done
                                by bringing out the best in those around him.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="column sm-12 md-6 lg-12">
                        <div class="about-section__main-img">
                            <img src="assets/img/test/about-section-main.jpg" alt="about">
                        </div>
                        <div class="about-section__decor" data-append="1024, .about-section__decor-block">
                            <div class="decor-text decor-font color-main after-element">
                                <div class="decor-text__content">Coaching is about teaching, and the best teachers never stop learning.</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column sm-12 lg-5">
            <div class="about-section__body">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="column sm-12 md-6 lg-12 sm-order-1 md-order-1 lg-order-2">
                        <div class="highlight_sm bordered-text">
                            His background and education have helped, of course, but it’s the journey that
                            provided the experience, exposed him to leading minds in multiple fields,
                            accelerated his own evolution, and forged his outlook.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="column sm-12 md-6 lg-12 sm-order-3 md-order-2 lg-order-1">
                        <div class="about-section__body-img">
                            <img src="assets/img/test/about-section-body.jpg" alt="about">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="column sm-12 sm-order-2 md-order-3 lg-order-3">
                        <div class="text after-element">
                            And it’s the outlook that has allowed him and his colleagues to succeedin
                            so many different settings, and to do so without sacrificing other facets
                            of their lives. It’s also what makes him such a versatile and compelling
                            speaker, easily making connections with local, regional, and international
                            audiences alike.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="column sm-12 md-7 lg-12 sm-order-4 md-order-4 lg-order-4">
                        <div class="about-section__highlight after-element">
                            His journey has included the digitization of an entire university campus,
                            a massively successful startup at Oman Mobile, a rapid transformation and
                            reinvigoration at Omantel, and a visionary strategy that made Tasneea Oil
                            & Gas Technology a model for industrial innovation and diversification.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="column sm-12 md-5 lg-12 sm-order-6 md-order-5 lg-order-5">
                        <div class="about-section__decor-block"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="column sm-12 sm-order-5 md-order-6 lg-order-6">
                        <div class="text">
                            More recently it sees him leading development of renewable energy,
                            helping industry harness the power of AI, pioneering new approaches
                            in higher education, and consulting with organizations seeking transformations
                            of their own. All while continuing to run Concordia Group, the holding and
                            investment firm he founded in I997.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
