<div class="primary-block">
    <div class="primary-block__decor">
        <div class="decor-text decor-font after-element color-main">
            <div class="decor-text__content">
                The biggest commitment you’ll ever to make is to yourself.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="primary-block__wrap">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="column sm-12 md-5 lg-6 md-order-2 lg-order-1">
                <div class="primary-block__img">
                    <img src="assets/img/test/primary-img.png" alt="">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column sm-12 md-7 lg-6 md-order-1 lg-order-2">
                <div class="primary-block__heading">
                    <h2 class="primary-block__title h2-font">Empathy, Commitment, and Meaningful Change</h2>
                    <div class="text">
                        Dr. Rawas teaches that empathy is the key to constructive human interactions,
                        especially when it comes to the sharing and absorption of new knowledge and
                        greater awareness. Whatever the capacity – leader, speaker, coach, or other –
                        the same rule applies: if you want to change minds, you have to touch hearts.
                        He also teaches that meaningful personal change is a process, not an event, and
                        making such changes requires lasting commitment. One of a coach’s most important
                        tasks, therefore, is to figure out what will resonate with individual coaches,
                        and that means caring enough to identify their core motivations and innermost concerns.
                    </div>
                    <div class="text">
                        These are powerful forces, and leaving them unexamined and/or unexploited can lead to undue
                        stress, anxiety, and other distractions that weaken job performance, erode physical and mental
                        health, and/or undermine key elements of our personal lives. By contrast, harnessing them as
                        sources of motivation, both conscious and subconscious, helps maintain the commitment and the
                        emotional intelligence required for people to evolve toward fulfillment.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column sm-12 lg-6  md-order-3 lg-order-3">
                <div class="primary-block__highlight highlight after-element">
                    Happiness is a wondrous thing, but fulfillment is both less scarce more sustainable,
                    and pursuing it generates its own rewards along the way. These qualities not only
                    make it a more realistic objective, but also a more useful one that sustains our
                    evolution, and fosters a healthier and more productive outlook on our daily work
                    responsibilities, long-term career goals, and overall purpose in life.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="fulfillment">
    <div class="row align-between">
        <div class="column sm-12 lg-6 xxl-5">
            <div class="fulfillment__heading">
                <h2 class="fulfillment__title h2-font">
                    Evolving Toward Fulfillment
                </h2>
                <div class="text">
                    Once we have a solid base of self-awareness and resolve to evolve toward fulfillment,
                    the journey makes every crisis an opportunity, and every setback a valuable lesson.
                    It should come as no surprise, too, that while outward happiness can mask deep-seated
                    dissatisfaction, fulfilled people are happier by default.
                </div>
                <div class="fulfillment__block">
                    <div class="border-block">
                        <div class="border-block__icon">
                            <img src="assets/img/heart.svg" alt="loyalty">
                        </div>
                        <div class="border-block__text">
                            A similar philosophy informs Dr. Rawas’ approach to workshops and public speaking,
                            one that emphasizes emotional intelligence, mutual empathy, and respect for
                            oneself and othersas conduits for better communication and teamwork. 
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    Whether one-on-one, in small  groups, or speaking to packed conference halls,
                    this approach helps individuals and organizations make lasting productivity
                    gains because it embraces what it means to be human – even as we rely increasingly
                    on artificial intelligence and other technologies that can be very disruptive for
                    workplaces that fail to make the necessary changes.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column sm-12 lg-6">
            <div class="fulfillment__content after-element">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="column sm-12 md-6 lg-12 md-order-2 lg-order-1">
                        <div class="fulfillment__img">
                            <img src="assets/img/test/fulfillment.jpg" alt="">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="column sm-12 md-6 lg-12 md-order-1 lg-order-2">
                        <div class="highlight_sm bordered-text">
                            Dr. Rawas did not arrive at such perspectives and insights overnight,
                            but he has developed a system that helps his coaches to get there
                            faster, learn more along the way, and appreciate every moment.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="column sm-12 md-order-3 lg-order-3">
                        <div class="text">
                            That is what drives his own fulfillment journey: the chance to leave a legacy
                            of well-rounded leaders, harmonious workplaces, and rewarding personal lives.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>